{"tid":2308588,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–細菌能否用來釀酒？","createTime":"2020-12-02T04:10:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T04:40:44.000Z","uid":38861,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f4948cbab1786682d774f09c978bb775d5b214dc","tid":2308588,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T04:10:35.000Z","msg":"酵母能夠將葡萄糖轉化成為酒精及二氧化碳， 酵母品種Saccharomyces cerevisiae亦因此亦成為了釀酒用的長年之選。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1kmtijk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1kmtijk.jpg&h=1b65a01d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n那麼除了酵母之外，細菌又可不可以用來釀酒呢?<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）事實上的確有細菌品種能夠轉化葡萄糖為酒精，Z.mobilis是其中一道例子，其產生酒精的效率比酵母高出3-5倍(Ref1)。<br />\n甚至乎，Z.mobilis 細菌的最高酒精產量可達97%(Ref2)，而S. cerevisiae則最高只能去到90-92%(Ref3)。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R6c0TSJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR6c0TSJ.jpg&h=009cf95a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可觀的表面數據擺在眼前，為何好像並不常聽見有人利用細菌來釀酒呢?<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）其中一道致命的原因，就是該細菌產生酒精的過程中，會產生帶有異味及混濁顏色的化學物（Acetylaldehyde及Sulfide Compounds），為酒精飲品帶來味覺及視覺的負面影響。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MLZ27cN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMLZ27cN.png&h=8ccba773&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以墨西哥的普逵酒 (Pulque)為例，其釀製過程中便會加入Z. mobilis，從圖中可以清楚見得到其視覺的衝突，至於味道究竟如何我就不太清楚......<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，基於Z. mobilis 無法在pH 3.75以下的環境繁殖，有不少的英國蘋果酒均會盡量將pH壓低3.5或以下，減低酒精受到Z. mobilis污染的機會。<br />\n<br />\n雖然細菌在產酒過程中會產生對飲用帶來負面效果的化學物，但基於其卓越的產酒效率，在工業用酒精的生產方面仍有其發揮空間。<br />\n同時間，亦難保有科學家會利用基因編輯技術，產生出一種高效率而又不會產生不良化合物的釀酒細菌品種。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\">like</span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2RY%2Fip2Wc62AYORpdIbS17M%3D&h=3bec23c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"orange\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2RY%2Fip2Wc62AYORpdIbS17M%3D&h=7fe862bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fpotatopigtongue%2F&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2RY%2Fip2Wc62AYORpdIbS17M%3D&h=9da32c95\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://academic.oup.com/femsle/article/145/3/301/605010\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Facademic.oup.com%2Ffemsle%2Farticle%2F145%2F3%2F301%2F605010&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2RY%2Fip2Wc62AYORpdIbS17M%3D&h=0f3dbb36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://academic.oup.com/femsle/article/145/3/301/605010</a><br />\nRef2:<a href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007%2F3540116982_2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flink.springer.com%2Fchapter%2F10.1007%252F3540116982_2&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2RY%2Fip2Wc62AYORpdIbS17M%3D&h=b94ebad8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007%2F3540116982_2</a><br />\nRef3:<a href=\"https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s00253-003-1393-5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flink.springer.com%2Farticle%2F10.1007%2Fs00253-003-1393-5&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2RY%2Fip2Wc62AYORpdIbS17M%3D&h=427d9063\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://link.springer.com/article/10.1007/s00253-003-1393-5</a>"},{"pid":"dd41aa3826a5fe76aabc9c25499d2baff6cd2214","tid":2308588,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T04:13:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fff1876477d712da5f82f2c68f4d5ff33502611","tid":2308588,"uid":54549,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T04:14:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c45c8b1f79e226b7aced97e5ebbd4f5ba235672","tid":2308588,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T04:18:06.000Z","msg":"kombucha係咪其中一個例子?<br />\n我見有啲放得耐酒精濃度就會上升"},{"pid":"7c89e4a25a3b3786d782191ef94af87b8d1e0fb3","tid":2308588,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7c45c8b1f79e226b7aced97e5ebbd4f5ba235672","tid":2308588,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T04:18:06.000Z","msg":"kombucha係咪其中一個例子?<br />\n我見有啲放得耐酒精濃度就會上升"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T04:24:46.000Z","msg":"都算係，不過佢係酵母加細菌而成。"},{"pid":"f58440085910cc7df31e382c6920dfa49c4066bd","tid":2308588,"uid":31254,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T04:28:33.000Z","msg":"會唔會將佢釀酒嘅gene clone 入酵母仲快手"},{"pid":"5d5bf226d66bae1130f09db034e29a74c212b56d","tid":2308588,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f58440085910cc7df31e382c6920dfa49c4066bd","tid":2308588,"uid":31254,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T04:28:33.000Z","msg":"會唔會將佢釀酒嘅gene clone 入酵母仲快手"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20